Class FilterModel

java.lang.Object
org.supsi.model.filters.FilterModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFilterModel
public class FilterModel extends Object implements IFilterModel
Represents the model for managing image filters and their pipeline. Provides methods to add, remove, and process filters, and tracks applied filters.
